    <ul style="margin: 0;">
      <li>Written Statement of Occupation Contract (within 14 days)</li>
      <li>Rent Smart Wales registration (landlord) and licence (agent)</li>
      <li>Energy Performance Certificate (EPC) - minimum rating E required</li>
      <li>Gas Safety Certificate (if property has gas) - renewed annually</li>
      <li>Electrical Installation Condition Report (EICR) - every 5 years</li>
      <li>Fitness for Human Habitation standard compliance</li>
    </ul>
